<title>Hʋpi okcha̱ya ta̱kla 'k osh ƲIT111</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hʋpi okcha̱ya ta̱kla 'k osh,
 Nana achukma hokʋno,
 Hʋpi chu̱kʋsh fehna hoka
 Isht il anukfihinlashke.

[V2]
 Pi̱ki ʋba binili kʋt
 Nana achukma fehna ka
 Pim ataiyahli tuk oka,
 Iloh aiokpahanchaske.

[V3]
 Ik pillo hosh nanta hona
 E toba he keyu hoke;
 Nana illi pulla kʋno,
 Hʋpilla chi̱ ka banoshke.

[V4]
 4 Nana hosh yakni paknaka
 Ilʋppa ahanta hokʋt
 Okcha̱yʋt bilia hi ʋt,
 Iksho kʋmohmi fehnʋshke.

[V5]
 Yʋmohmi pulla hoh kia,
 Pimi shilombish okʋto,
 Nitak nanta ihinli wa;
 Okcha̱yʋt bilia yoke.

[V6]
 Pi̱ki ʋba pulla kak o̱,
 Iloh im antia tukmʋt
 A hʋp ihinli hoh kia,
 Ik hʋp illo choyuhmashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Funeral: &quot;What man is he that liveth and shall not see death?&quot;</aka>
</song>